text: Xenorhabdus mauleonii is a bacterium from the genus of Xenorhabdus which has been isolated from an undescribed Steinernema species.Deutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen UniProt == References == == Further reading == * * ==External links== *Type strain of Xenorhabdus mauleonii at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase Category:Bacteria described in 2006
